{"tid":590431,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[💩] 吸糞車出事邊行邊漏 屎味籠罩成個北區","createTime":"2018-03-12T15:20:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-12T15:30:16.000Z","uid":8420,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2b92fdf2d81107faf9685d1ea3e9da2d3e37525d","tid":590431,"uid":8420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T15:20:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/232001_d0afa529da0df1b41646f50a77712bac.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F232001_d0afa529da0df1b41646f50a77712bac.png&h=ca061d5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n晚上9時許，一部吸糞車駛經粉嶺沙頭角公路綠悠軒時壞車，拖車到場拖走吸糞車時，大量糞便液體不斷流出，散滿公路上，現場臭氣熏天，籠罩整個北區，遠至上水太平邨都聞到。<br />\n<br />\n居於粉嶺的網民晚上紛紛留言稱「臭到想嘔」，甚至有距離現場約2公里外的太平邨居民亦指聞到惡臭，事件旋即引起熱議。有網民笑稱「遍地黄金」，亦有人留言指「啱啱食緊飯囉&hellip;臭到食唔落」。<br />\n<br />\n網民洗版︰<br />\n<br />\nKim Choy︰開頭我以爲自己踩屎，一路行一路有屎味跟住自己，行到出聯和墟先發現問題唔係自己<br />\nSinsin Tsoi︰綠悠軒 好大陣臭味 真係好想嘔<br />\nSarine Habibi︰天平至沙頭角超臭，救命<br />\nKaman Ho︰味入晒屋，全屋閂晒窗 <br />\nTobias Chan︰個個都以為自己踩屎，個個係度望鞋底，笑死我喇"},{"pid":"1c6894be7b81c2dd5fecedbf5f49600689bdedb3","tid":590431,"uid":73586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T15:21:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5848bd310a6e3bc9469f2f0f5221ecef982aed33","tid":590431,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T15:22:17.000Z","msg":"正啊"},{"pid":"3e66b3bad1aff9b22e36016ebc8405d21f66a668","tid":590431,"uid":29887,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T15:22:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/jirbkWn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FjirbkWn.jpg&h=7e34940d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"81fa4bde459b7475db7ce52e3cb34f8790b188d3","tid":590431,"uid":8478,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T15:22:52.000Z","msg":"邊有可能呀太平邨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n天平邨就話啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bf2a87fdc0c4bedcd3b39260a2cade8ca027fe8","tid":590431,"uid":169468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T15:22:53.000Z","msg":"Kim Choy︰開頭我以爲自己踩屎，一路行一路有屎味跟住自己，行到出聯和墟先發現問題唔係自己<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd99fb5591547e29c6657f80fed04d1f26071977","tid":590431,"uid":90863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T15:22:56.000Z","msg":"個post都有陣屎味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de781b81c4ffa14a968521720cd3bccbdf9e0d0b","tid":590431,"uid":126766,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T15:23:03.000Z","msg":"抵啦<br />\n北區<br />\n狗都唔屌"},{"pid":"8b2dd3ec222f2fb0a97b62ffb5b59863e147f5e0","tid":590431,"uid":72621,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T15:23:54.000Z","msg":"屌頭先坐架44臭撚到"},{"pid":"1e81a76050f8aeedfbba1671b6390c2a36ff450f","tid":590431,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T15:24:39.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"3c6c353c3e3ff7a5ce20ef49edf9a845a4b39d72","tid":590431,"uid":162441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T15:25:46.000Z","msg":"有咩所謂，香港人都習慣晒對住啲屎啦（建制派果班）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d0a90616700801edb1de565c06b960d5910a24f","tid":590431,"uid":160807,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3c6c353c3e3ff7a5ce20ef49edf9a845a4b39d72","tid":